    "description": "If you're a passionate Department Manager with drive and ambition, Godrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates in Coimbatore is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Godrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates:\nGodrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Godrej Interio Asia Pacific Associates!",
